{"tid":1032250,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"成日收到啲自稱marketing 公司嘅電話","createTime":"2019-02-22T08:27:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T18:33:49.000Z","uid":46200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cb40d44f5d51edd406726a58c5a403e2fa6d65f3","tid":1032250,"uid":46200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T08:27:51.000Z","msg":"呢個月已經第二次收到一個自稱marketing 公司嘅電話<br />\n佢講得出我嘅姓，仲話我以前留過資料話想做part time job<br />\n但我完全冇印象我留過任何電話<br />\n亦一直無意欲番任何part time 賺錢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一打嚟就話：「請問係咪姓X？」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「係。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「我地係間marketing 公司，之前你申請嘅part time job 我地會安排一個面試俾你。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「我冇印象我留過資料揾part time 喎，我幾時留㗎？」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「睇番資料應該係年幾兩年前留嘅。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「不如你講下間公司係做咩嘅？」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「我地係間marketing 公司揾promoter，以job計錢，一單一千至三千蚊，freelance 形式去做，入到嚟係有head leader 帶。」<br />\n之後我話冇興趣之類就完咗。<br />\n<br />\n有冇人都有收過呢類電話？<br />\n係咪咩新型騙局？定我以前on99留過電話都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a021e4f958b8db772ebe39156fe19d39e4f399","tid":1032250,"uid":83094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T08:58:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9d0fe8e9cb74e0b5298efd68b081b14fcf631576","tid":1032250,"uid":235224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T18:30:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb3569e914fa6f63884e54a50520a539151d761f","tid":1032250,"uid":235224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2